    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and reliability, having been kept in consistent, high-functioning order. The exterior paint holds a deep shine, though close inspection reveals a few minor road-pebble chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel well\u2014typical of a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free; the leather seats remain firm and supportive, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s entry point. All interior technology, from the premium sound system to the dual-zone climate control, operates exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with no leaks or unusual noises. It comes with a documented service history, including a recent transmission flush and a fresh set of spark plugs. The tires are high-quality all-seasons with plenty of miles left in the tread. This is a dependable, well-cared-for machine ready for its next chapter.",
